title: New: Japanese Wallpaper – Between Friends (Feat. Jesse Davidson
content:
Beautiful little collaboration between two of Australia’s fastest rising stars, 17 year old producer Japanese Wallpaper (Gab Strum) and 18 year old Adelaide singer Jesse Davidson.

Having just won triple J Unearthed’s ‘High’ competition, being nominated alongside the likes of Baro, Azura and Lupa J, it’s a real indication of the sort of talent that Australia is nurturing right now. Between Friends is a gorgeously delicate number,  that’ll no doubt see an endless number of remixes coming from it. Check it out below.
